adding:0px;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑&quot;&gt;思，雨雪霏霏..&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑&quot;&gt;读了四年中文，最后才发现学的最多的是东拼西凑，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微软雅黑&quot;&gt;ctrl c + ctrl v .. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微软雅黑&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:微软雅黑&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://r.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V14Rn7Yq084Tl5/OeKkAp81lwafjB3g5gC4L*gShAIBZ41ZsqsO6aDyXS0!/o/dKbyBWD0JAAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;bo=GAIgA54C6AMBAGk!&amp;amp;su=1246531617&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;17&quot; alt=&quot;图片&quot; src=&quot;http://r.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V14Rn7Yq084Tl5/OeKkAp81lwafjB3g5gC4L*gShAIBZ41ZsqsO6aDyXS0%21/o/dKbyBWD0JAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=GAIgA54C6AMBAGk%21&amp;su=1246531617&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-9&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://r.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V14Rn7Yq084Tl5/OS0dUqrf2ED3a9ZH9WtnhUdyQLHb9BvUuPGFIncEfiA!/o/dIlaal9YIAAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;bo=KgIgA7QC6AMBAHE!&amp;amp;su=14560881&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;18&quot; alt=&quot;图片&quot; src=&quot;http://r.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/V14Rn7Yq084Tl5/OS0dUqrf2ED3a9ZH9WtnhUdyQLHb9BvUuPGFIncEfiA%21/o/dIlaal9YIAAA&amp;ek=1&amp;kp=1&amp;pt=0&amp;bo=KgIgA7QC6AMBAHE%21&amp;su=14560881&amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;rf=2-9&quot;/&g